大声点
Talk louder!

4
00:03:55,660 --> 00:03:57,494
我听不到
I can't hear you!

5
00:03:57,620 --> 00:03:59,246
嘿,喂!
Hey, hello!

6
00:03:59,330 --> 00:04:01,957
喂!我听不到你说话
Hello! I can't hear you!

7
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:21,139
5个
Five.

8
00:04:28,979 --> 00:04:30,688
不知道
I don't know.

9
00:04:33,233 --> 00:04:34,984
我不知道
I don't know.

10
00:06:46,512 --> 00:06:49,556
让她精神集中点! 我来了
Get her in focus! Here I come!

11
00:06:55,269 --> 00:06:57,937
开门,糟了
Open up! Shit!

12
00:07:06,278 --> 00:07:09,113
上帝啊,你怎么--?
Jesus H. Christ!
What are you--?

13
00:07:11,658 --> 00:07:14,702
怎么了?
What happened?

14
00:07:21,166 --> 00:07:24,126
现在他有压力了,他拿到了球
Now he's got pressure.
He has a receiver!

15
00:07:25,586 --> 00:07:29,047
当需要放松时
When it's time to relax

16
00:07:29,131 --> 00:07:31,716
一罐啤酒足矣
One beer stands clear

17
00:07:32,342 --> 00:07:34,301
哦,该死的
Oh, damn it!

18
00:07:46,437 --> 00:07:48,146
特悌?
Tweety?

19
00:07:57,029 --> 00:08:00,615
哦,该死,特悌,你就不能再等一个教学日吗?
Oh, shit, Tweety! Couldn't you
have waited for a school day?

20
00:08:06,204 --> 00:08:09,581
请不要
Won't you please

21
00:08:09,623 --> 00:08:11,207
请不要
Please won't you be

22
00:08:11,333 --> 00:08:13,459
这家伙是谁?
Who the hell is this guy?

23
00:08:13,585 --> 00:08:15,878
发生什么了?
What the hell's going on?

24
00:08:18,506 --> 00:08:21,008
富勒里, 怎么回事?
Freeling, what's goin' on here?

25
00:08:21,050 --> 00:08:24,094
我道歉
我邻居也是同一个频段
I apologize!
My neighbor's on the same remote!

26
00:08:26,346 --> 00:08:29,640
我为这场比赛连命都赌上了,你开玩笑吧
I bet my life on this game!
Are you kiddin' me?

27
00:08:31,350 --> 00:08:34,644
本,我们那正在放一场精彩的球赛
Hi, Ben. We got a good
football game goin' on here.

28
00:08:34,686 --> 00:08:37,354
我的孩子要看"罗杰先生"
My kids wanna watch
"Mr. Rogers."

29
00:08:37,397 --> 00:08:40,983
我不在乎你要看什么,你就算是可怜可怜我们
I don't care what you're watchin'!
Just show some mercy with that thing!

30
00:08:44,361 --> 00:08:46,112
别啊,史迪夫
Come on, Steve!

31
00:08:46,238 --> 00:08:47,405
把你的遥控器拿开
Move your set.

32
00:08:51,367 --> 00:08:54,369
- 拿开,本
- 就这样,别换了
- Move yours, Ben.
- There it is. Don't move.

33
00:09:57,714 --> 00:10:00,132
特悌不喜欢这个味道
Tweety doesn't like that smell.

34
00:10:00,175 --> 00:10:03,010
甜心,特悌闻不到什么味道
Sweetheart,
Tweety can't smell a thing.

35
00:10:03,052 --> 00:10:04,720
给他献朵花吧
Put a flower with him.

36
00:10:04,845 --> 00:10:06,763
一朵花?
A flower?

37
00:10:16,438 --> 00:10:18,773
为了他生气的时候
For when he's hungry.

38
00:10:22,318 --> 00:10:25,320
为了他不再孤单
For when he's lonely.

39
00:10:27,614 --> 00:10:30,032
为了他将度过的长夜.
For when it's nighttime.

40
00:10:37,498 --> 00:10:39,624
没事了
Oh, it's okay.

41
00:11:15,947 --> 00:11:18,699
现在我躺下长眠...
Now I lay me down to sleep...

42
00:11:18,824 --> 00:11:21,909
我祈祷主宽恕我的灵魂
I pray the Lord my soul to keep.

43
00:11:21,952 --> 00:11:23,911
- 哦,天哪
- 忍着点
- Oh, brother.
- Stifle it.

44
00:11:24,954 --> 00:11:27,372
如果我在醒来之际死去...
If I should die before I wake...

45
00:11:27,498 --> 00:11:28,915
会的
It did.

46
00:11:28,958 --> 00:11:31,626
我请求主带走我的灵魂
I pray the Lord my soul to take.

47
00:11:31,668 --> 00:11:34,253
你这样很可爱,很可爱
That was lovely.
Lovely, honey.

48
00:11:34,779 --> 00:11:37,656
妈,等尸体腐烂之后能把骨头挖出来吗?
Mom, when it rots,
can we dig up the bones?

49
00:11:37,698 --> 00:11:41,534
罗比,你就不能从树上下来?
Robbie! Will you come
on down out of the tree?

50
00:11:41,618 --> 00:11:42,535
E. Buzz!
E. Buzz!

51
00:11:42,619 --> 00:11:45,246
我们现在能养条金鱼了吗
Can I have a goldfish now?

52
00:11:50,959 --> 00:11:53,377
来吃啊
Come and get it.

53
00:11:53,420 --> 00:11:55,713
来吃啊
Come and get it.

54
00:12:49,467 --> 00:12:51,135
你把他们喂的太饱了
You're overfeeding them.

55
00:12:51,135 --> 00:12:54,137
二十二和二十三还想要
Tweety Two and Tweety Three
want seconds.

56
00:12:54,137 --> 00:12:56,972
你知道怎么回事吗,你喂的太多了?
You know what happens
when you overfeed goldfish?

57
00:12:59,350 --> 00:13:03,061
他们要长成...鲨鱼
They grow up to be... sharks!

58
00:13:08,024 --> 00:13:09,900
晚安
Good night.

59
00:13:14,571 --> 00:13:17,073
妈妈.有大风暴要来了
Mom, there's a big storm
headed this way.

60
00:13:17,198 --> 00:13:19,783
如果你们快点
风暴在你们入睡之后才会来
You'll be asleep by the time
it gets here if you hurry.

61
00:13:19,909 --> 00:13:22,327
来,到被子里去
Come on. In you go.

62
00:13:26,206 --> 00:13:28,165
晚安,宝贝
Good night, sweetie.

63
00:13:29,208 --> 00:13:31,626
好,关灯了
Okay, lights out.

64
00:13:31,669 --> 00:13:33,754
灯灭了!
Closet light!

65
00:13:33,879 --> 00:13:35,755
我的错
My fault.

66
00:13:35,881 --> 00:13:38,299
开灯,妈妈
Turn it on, Mommy!

67
00:13:45,472 --> 00:13:46,931
够了吧?
That enough?

68
00:13:48,892 --> 00:13:51,102
- 行吧?
- 晚安,妈
- Okay?
- Good night, Mom.

69
00:13:51,227 --> 00:13:52,769
晚安.妈妈
Night, Mommy.

70
00:13:59,234 --> 00:14:00,943
晚安
Good night.

71
00:14:09,617 --> 00:14:11,827
我死了或是疯了
Either I'm dead or I'm crazy.

72
00:14:11,911 --> 00:14:14,329
皮特,你没有疯
You're not crazy, Pete.

73
00:14:15,247 --> 00:14:17,540
那你是说我死了?
You mean I'm dead?

74
00:14:18,667 --> 00:14:20,251
我--
I'm--

75
00:14:22,920 --> 00:14:25,922
你是说--
你是说这是好事?
You mean--
You mean this is for good?

76
00:14:25,965 --> 00:14:27,674
梦游啊
Sleepwalking.

77
00:14:27,716 --> 00:14:31,510
晚上的梦游症,你不知道吗?
Nocturnal somnambulism.
You know what?

78
00:14:31,553 --> 00:14:34,680
我跟你打赌,这是遗传的
I will bet you anything
it's genetic.

79
00:14:36,849 --> 00:14:40,101
卡罗尔昨晚就是,整个星期的晚上都在梦游
I mean, Carol Anne last night
and all last week.

80
00:14:41,227 --> 00:14:43,395
我十岁的时候也是
And me when I was ten.

81
00:14:45,981 --> 00:14:48,941
- 你能搞定这个吗?
- 好
- Would you deal with this?
- Sure.

82
00:14:53,404 --> 00:14:54,988
你知道..
You know...

83
00:14:56,282 --> 00:14:59,284
一次我梦游外出...
once I slept-walked four blocks...

84
00:15:00,410 --> 00:15:04,413
在一个伙计的车的后座上睡着了
and I fell asleep
in the back of this guy's car.

85
00:15:05,748 --> 00:15:09,709
你一直开着车,去工作也没发现我
He drove all the way to work
before discovering me.

86
00:15:09,751 --> 00:15:12,586
天,然后我醒来了,开始狂叫
God, I woke up,
I started screaming.

87
00:15:12,712 --> 00:15:15,672
人们跑过来,叫了警察
People came running, called the cops.

88
00:15:15,715 --> 00:15:19,176
警察把这个可怜的花花公子带到市区
The cops took
this poor dude downtown.

89
00:15:20,761 --> 00:15:23,179
- 我父亲, Ed--
-Big.
- My father, Ed--
- Big.

90
00:15:24,722 --> 00:15:28,475
Big Ed 还检查了我有没有受伤,
有没有被侮辱
Big Ed has me examined
for bruises and hickeys.

91
00:15:28,601 --> 00:15:31,853
天啊,真是太尴尬了
God, I was so embarrassed!

92
00:15:35,356 --> 00:15:37,732
哦,天,史迪夫
Oh, shit, Steve.

93
00:15:37,858 --> 00:15:40,318
如果我们挖个水池.你知道...
What if we dig the pool,
you know...

94
00:15:40,444 --> 00:15:44,030
在没有水之前,卡罗尔梦游时掉进去了会怎么样?
and Carol Anne sleepwalks and falls
into it before there's any water?

95
00:15:44,072 --> 00:15:46,198
哦,亲爱的,别这样
Oh, honey, no.

96
00:15:46,324 --> 00:15:50,077
甜心,你滑过3米长的滑板吗?
Have you ever dove off
a three-meter board, sweetheart?

97
00:15:50,202 --> 00:15:53,663
- 三米是多少?
- 十英尺
- What's three meters?
- It's about ten feet.

98
00:15:53,747 --> 00:15:58,459
我们把水池挖的离屋子近点
这样孩子们就可以从屋顶上跳下去了
Let's dig the pool closer to the house
and let the kids jump off the roof.

99
00:15:58,459 --> 00:16:01,044
别,亲爱的
No, honey, honey, honey.

100
00:16:01,170 --> 00:16:04,923
甜心,3米长的滑板就像个空气袋
A three-meter board is like
an air pocket, sweetheart.

101
00:16:05,048 --> 00:16:08,759
当你跳水时就像自由落体一样?
When you dive off,
it's like free-falling, okay?

102
00:16:08,801 --> 00:16:12,929
你要站好位置,3米远
You gotta get your feet in position.
Three meters.

103
00:16:12,971 --> 00:16:15,514
亲爱的,你的跳水生涯已经结束了
Honey, your diving days are over.

104
00:16:15,515 --> 00:16:18,642
我们在谈论奥林匹克,达尼,知道吧
We're talkin' Olympics,
Diane, okay?

105
00:16:20,102 --> 00:16:23,062
让我看看你的起跳位置
Let me see your tuck position.

106
00:16:23,188 --> 00:16:26,774
我们像天鹅一样展开
We can jackknife into the swan.

107
00:16:28,901 --> 00:16:30,777
收缩,转身...
Twist, turn...

108
00:16:30,820 --> 00:16:33,322
然后跳出去
and splash!

109
00:16:35,991 --> 00:16:38,785
亲爱的,去鹦鹉螺号是对的
Honey, it's right to
the Nautilus machine.

110
00:16:38,826 --> 00:16:41,953
看这个,收缩,伸展
Look at this, honey.
Before, after.

111
00:16:42,079 --> 00:16:44,289
收缩,伸展
Before, after.
Before, after.

112
00:17:54,723 --> 00:17:57,433
- 别了
- 我爱你
- Don't.
- I love you.

113
00:18:07,860 --> 00:18:11,488
天,我喜欢你说脏话的样子
Oh, God, I love it
when you talk dirty!

114
00:18:15,199 --> 00:18:16,741
风暴越来越近了
Storm is coming closer.

115
00:18:19,494 --> 00:18:20,911
嘿, 搭档.
Hey, partner.

116
00:18:20,954 --> 00:18:22,330
嘿,亲爱的
Hi, honey.

117
00:18:22,455 --> 00:18:24,873
一切还好吧?
Is everything okay?

118
00:18:28,460 --> 00:18:30,378
在打雷
It's thundering.

119
00:18:30,462 --> 00:18:33,297
来,起来
Come on. Hop up.

120
00:18:35,466 --> 00:18:40,053
你是风,我是风中的羽毛
跟妈妈说晚安
I'm the wind and you're the feather.
Say good night to Mom.

121
00:18:40,178 --> 00:18:42,513
- 晚安.妈妈
- 晚安,宝贝
- Good night, Mom.
- Good night, sweetheart.

122
00:18:47,351 --> 00:18:49,102
走咯
Here we go.

123
00:18:56,275 --> 00:18:58,526
我不喜欢那根树
I don't like the tree, Dad.

124
00:18:59,695 --> 00:19:03,197
那是根老树了,在这很久了
That's an old tree.
It's been around here a long time.

125
00:19:03,239 --> 00:19:05,907
在我的朋友成为邻居前就在这
It was here before my company
built the neighborhood.

126
00:19:05,950 --> 00:19:07,909
我不喜欢它的手臂
I don't like its arms.

127
00:19:07,952 --> 00:19:12,080
- 它知道我住在这里,是吧?
- 它知道我们的一切
- It knows I live here, doesn't it?
- It knows everything about us.

128
00:19:12,122 --> 00:19:15,249
那就是我在它旁边建房子的缘故,
它能保护我们
That's why I built the house next to it,
so it could protect us.

129
00:19:15,375 --> 00:19:18,627
你,卡罗尔,达纳,你妈妈和我
You and Carol Anne
and Dana and your mom and me.

130
00:19:18,669 --> 00:19:21,838
这是根老而智慧的树
It's a very wise old tree.

131
00:19:21,922 --> 00:19:25,424
它看着我,它知道我在这
It looks at me.
It knows I live here.

132
00:19:28,511 --> 00:19:30,596
我想,风暴会掠过我们而去
I think the storm's gonna pass us.

133
00:19:30,679 --> 00:19:32,263
你怎么知道的?
How do you know?

134
00:19:32,306 --> 00:19:35,308
我能算出
'Cause I can count.

135
00:19:35,391 --> 00:19:37,601
你知道怎么做?
You know what you do?

136
00:19:37,685 --> 00:19:39,978
看到闪电时...
When you see the lightning...

137
00:19:39,979 --> 00:19:43,398
就开始数,知道听到雷声
you count 'til you hear the thunder.

138
00:19:43,523 --> 00:19:47,025
如果数的多说明风暴远了
If you can count higher each time,
that means the storm's movin' away.

139
00:19:48,277 --> 00:19:50,612
想试试吗?
Wanna try it?

140
00:19:51,530 --> 00:19:53,531
需要一些闪电啊
We need some lightning.

141
00:19:55,325 --> 00:19:57,284
等等,来了
Wait. It's comin'.

142
00:20:02,581 --> 00:20:06,542
好,开始数,1,2,3
Okay, count.
One, two, three.

143
00:20:08,336 --> 00:20:13,465
跟你打赌,下次肯定可以数到4或者5
Next time, you'll be able to count
to at least four or five. Bet you.

144
00:20:13,549 --> 00:20:15,300
爸,找你的
Daddy, it's for you.

145
00:20:15,342 --> 00:20:17,593
让他们留个信,亲爱的
Tell them to take
a message, sweet pea.

146
00:20:17,635 --> 00:20:19,469
我爸让你们留话
My dad wants to take a message.

147
00:20:24,308 --> 00:20:25,725
晚安
Night.

148
00:20:29,062 --> 00:20:31,021
太热了
It's too hot.

149
00:20:31,063 --> 00:20:34,190
好,晚安,小天使
Okay. Night, angel.

150
00:20:34,274 --> 00:20:37,276
- 做个好梦,好吗?
- 晚安,爸
- Happy dreams, okay?
- Night, Daddy.

151
00:20:40,863 --> 00:20:42,155
1...
One...

152
00:20:42,198 --> 00:20:43,740
2...
two...

153
00:20:43,866 --> 00:20:45,450
3--
three--

154
00:20:53,374 --> 00:20:56,459
我没有.少来了
I did not. Come on!

155
00:20:57,794 --> 00:21:00,212
- 晚安,达尼
- 晚安.爸
- Good night, Dana.
- Good night, Dad.

156
00:21:03,049 --> 00:21:05,217
- 别打电话了,达尼
- 好的,爸
- Get off the phone, Dana.
- Okay, Dad.

157
00:21:12,515 --> 00:21:13,891
1...
One...

158
00:21:13,933 --> 00:21:15,058
2--
two--

159
00:21:15,059 --> 00:21:17,102
3...
Three...

160
00:21:17,227 --> 00:21:18,186
4--
four--

161
00:21:18,228 --> 00:21:19,353
5--
Five--

162
00:24:29,681 --> 00:24:32,099
他们来了
They're here.

163
00:24:44,693 --> 00:24:48,529
听我说,杰夫
不,我不开玩笑
Listen to me, Jeff.
No, I'm not kidding.

164
00:24:48,572 --> 00:24:52,617
我知道,但谁在6.5级的风暴中还睡的着呢?
I know. How could anybody
sleep through a 6.5?

165
00:24:52,700 --> 00:24:56,703
卧室受到损害,碎片到处都是
There was damage. Yeah, the bedroom.
There's stuff in pieces all over.

166
00:24:59,456 --> 00:25:03,167
我们在听收音机,但是什么都没有
We're listening to the radio.
There's nothing on the radio at all.

167
00:25:07,838 --> 00:25:10,882
你真讨厌,让我疯了
You are so obnoxious!
You drive me nuts!

168
00:25:12,759 --> 00:25:13,884
力场
Force field.

169
00:25:14,010 --> 00:25:16,887
- 你真讨厌
- 击中我的鼻子了
- You are so obnoxious.
- Got my nose.

170
00:25:18,430 --> 00:25:20,932
这意味着战争,我也这么认为
This means war, and I mean it!

171
00:25:23,059 --> 00:25:26,561
- 嘿,看着点
- 宝贝,你应该把食物咀嚼10次
- Hey, watch out.
- Honey, chew your food ten times.

172
00:25:26,604 --> 00:25:28,730
你像个呕吐袋
You're a big barf bag.

173
00:25:28,772 --> 00:25:30,940
你才像
You're a doggie bag.

174
00:25:32,317 --> 00:25:34,777
- 我不吃了
- 你要吃的
- I won't eat it.
- There you go.

175
00:25:36,028 --> 00:25:39,197
甜心,昨晚你说 ''他们来了''之时--
Sweetheart, last night
when you said, "They're here"--

176
00:25:39,323 --> 00:25:41,491
我能把金鱼带到学校去吗?
Can I take my goldfish to school?

177
00:25:41,616 --> 00:25:45,786
也许出问题的地方正好在房子下
但那些不用发出尖叫声吧?
Maybe the fault line runs directly under
our house. Wouldn't that be a scream?

178
00:25:45,786 --> 00:25:48,204
天花板一直在我床头响
The ceiling got crumbs
